title: Live commentary, do or die: Blue Jays-Royals in Game 5
text:
Live commentary, do or die: Blue Jays-Royals in Game 5 By Vancouver Sun October 21, 2015 1:09 PM Kansas City Royals Ben Zobrist (left) avoids Toronto Blue Jays’ Jose Bautista to turn a double play during the sixth inning of Game 4 of the American League Championship Series in Toronto on Tuesday. Photograph by: Darren Calabrese , THE CANADIAN PRESS
